'''Leinil Francis Yu''' is a [[Wikipedia:Filipinos|Filipino]] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] artist who provided covers for [[Dark Horse Comics]]' ''[[Star Wars Tales 10]]'' and ''[[Star Wars Tales 15]]''.

He has later drawn variant covers for two issues of the [[Star Wars Book I: Skywalker Strikes|first story arc]] of [[Marvel Comics]]' relaunched [[Star Wars (2015)|''Star Wars'']] comic series and for the [[Lando 1|first issue]] of the [[Star Wars: Lando (comic series)|''Lando'']] miniseries. Yu has also penciled [[Darth Vader Annual 1|''Darth Vader Annual'' 1]] and the [[Star Wars Book IV: Rebel Jail|fourth arc]] of the ''Star Wars'' series.

His work includes Marvel's [[W:c:marvel:Wolverine Vol 2|''Wolverine'']], [[W:c:marvel:X-Men Vol 2|''X-Men'']], [[W:c:marvel:Secret Invasion Vol 1|''Secret Invasion'']], and [[W:c:marvel:Ultimate Wolverine vs. Hulk Vol 1|''Ultimate Wolverine vs. Hulk'']], as well as the [[W:c:marvel:Superior Vol 1|''Superior'']] miniseries published under the [[W:c:marvel:Icon Comics|Icon Comics]] imprint.

